{# ==================== WHAT YOU GET ==================== #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container-x">
    <p class="section-kicker">What you get with us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title mb-10">Built around you, every single week.</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
      <div class="card"><h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Weekly tracking</h3><p class="text-brand-off/70 text-sm">Weekly data capture so we can tune your training and nutrition as your body changes.</p></div>
